User (Frontend)
   │
   │ 1️⃣ Enters details in Issuance Form (Name, Email, EmployeeID)
   │
   ▼
Issuance Page (React)
   │
   │ 2️⃣ Sends POST request to Issuance API
   │    POST /api/submit-details
   │
   ▼
Issuance API (Express + TS)
   │
   │ 3️⃣ Controller receives request
   │
   │ 4️⃣ Checks in issuanceCredentials.json
   │      └─ If duplicate (employeeID OR email) → return error
   │      └─ Else → create new credential object
   │
   │ 5️⃣ Saves credential to JSON file (data/issuanceCredentials.json)
   │
   │ 6️⃣ Returns response to frontend
   │      └─ success: true / false
   │      └─ message: "Credential issued successfully" or "Duplicate found"
   │      └─ worker: "worker-1"
   │
   ▼
Frontend (React)
   │
   │ 7️⃣ Shows success or error message to user
   │
   └─────────────────────────────┐
                                 │
User (Verification Form)         │
   │                             │
   │ 8️⃣ Enters credential to verify (employeeID or Email)
   │
   ▼
Verification Page (React)
   │
   │ 9️⃣ Sends POST request to Verification API
   │    POST /api/verify
   │
   ▼
Verification API (Express + TS)
   │
   │ 10️⃣ Controller reads issuanceCredentials.json
   │
   │ 11️⃣ Checks if credential exists
   │      └─ If exists → return success + worker + timestamp + credential
   │      └─ If not → return failure + worker + timestamp
   │
   ▼
Frontend (React)
   │
   │ 12️⃣ Displays verification result to user
   │       └─ Valid or Invalid
   │       └─ Worker ID
   │       └─ Timestamp
